sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staff as Staff or Head
    participant Web as Web Application
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Doc as Document Service
    participant Store as File Storage
    participant DB as Application Database
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Staff->>Web: Upload document for workflow step
    Web->>API: Send file and metadata
    API->>Doc: Validate project, step, and file type
    Doc->>DB: Read latest document version
    DB-->>Doc: Current version number
    Doc->>Store: Store file binary
    Store-->>Doc: File storage location
    Doc->>DB: Create document version record
    DB-->>Doc: Version saved
    Doc->>Audit: Record uploader, timestamp, and action
    Audit->>DB: Save audit log entry
    DB-->>Audit: Audit saved
    Doc-->>API: Upload result with version
    API-->>Web: Return updated document list
    Web-->>Staff: Show uploaded version
